WEBVTT

00:00:55.479 --> 00:00:56.000
Lawyer Luo

00:00:56.240 --> 00:00:56.960
Fang Qiu is awake.

00:00:57.479 --> 00:00:59.119
He just called about the will.

00:01:00.119 --> 00:01:00.880
Can he move?

00:01:01.240 --> 00:01:02.079
He says he can.

00:01:02.520 --> 00:01:02.920
Good.

00:01:03.359 --> 00:01:03.920
Notify everyone.

00:01:04.120 --> 00:01:05.200
The will is to be read tomorrow morning.

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:05.920
Yes.

00:02:38.240 --> 00:02:38.960
Detective Qi.

00:02:39.439 --> 00:02:40.319
Are you in there?

00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:43.599
Detective Qi.

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:46.800
Detective Qi, are you all right?

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:03.439
What?

00:03:03.879 --> 00:03:05.000
Is there a time limit for the bathroom?

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:05.479
Sorry.

00:03:05.879 --> 00:03:06.719
I was worried about you...

00:03:06.759 --> 00:03:07.879
...that something happened in there.

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:11.199
I've had an upset stomach lately.

00:03:25.919 --> 00:03:27.479
Has anyone else visited in the last couple of days?

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:28.319
No.

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:30.840
Only Miss Li gave me a call.

00:03:32.080 --> 00:03:32.639
What about?

00:03:33.199 --> 00:03:34.759
Just a simple check-in.

00:03:42.319 --> 00:03:43.000
Phone.

00:03:45.639 --> 00:03:46.159
Hello.

00:03:48.680 --> 00:03:49.360
He's awake.

00:03:53.159 --> 00:03:54.400
Then I won't disturb you.

00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:54.719
Okay.

00:03:54.719 --> 00:03:55.479
I'm leaving now. I'll see you out.

00:03:56.039 --> 00:03:56.360
No need.

00:03:58.719 --> 00:03:59.240
By the way.

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:01.560
Has anyone else visited in the last couple of days?

00:04:02.039 --> 00:04:03.400
Didn't you just ask that?

00:04:04.599 --> 00:04:04.960
Right.

00:04:05.639 --> 00:04:06.360
My memory is bad.

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:13.199
Wait for my lawyer.

00:04:13.479 --> 00:04:15.680
Otherwise, I won't say a word.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:18.800
Watch your attitude.

00:04:22.519 --> 00:04:23.720
As for me...

00:04:23.720 --> 00:04:24.759
My visit is simple.

00:04:28.279 --> 00:04:28.879
There's no need...

00:04:28.879 --> 00:04:30.279
...for your lawyer to be present.

00:04:31.639 --> 00:04:32.560
I just want to ask you...

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:34.600
...you and Lin Niannian...

00:04:35.879 --> 00:04:36.759
...are you sure you don't know each other?

00:04:37.759 --> 00:04:39.079
Of course I don't know her.

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:43.759
Mind if I sit?

00:04:49.279 --> 00:04:51.079
In Difu's cloud drive...

00:04:51.079 --> 00:04:52.959
...we found many photos of her and Lin Niannian.

00:04:54.160 --> 00:04:54.600
Look.

00:04:54.879 --> 00:04:56.199
This isn't just once or twice.

00:04:56.959 --> 00:04:58.519
We found you in them as well.

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:00.600
Hiking.

00:05:04.120 --> 00:05:04.759
The beach.

00:05:05.079 --> 00:05:05.800
And you...

00:05:06.319 --> 00:05:07.279
...are her brother-in-law.

00:05:07.720 --> 00:05:09.040
It's not strange for you to go out with her.

00:05:10.519 --> 00:05:12.120
But Lin Niannian is her good friend.

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:14.720
So why do you insist...

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:15.439
...that you don't know her?

00:05:21.279 --> 00:05:22.560
Wait for my lawyer to arrive.

00:05:24.639 --> 00:05:27.199
These foreign influencers who took photos with her...

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:28.639
Ever since they appeared on camera,

00:05:28.839 --> 00:05:30.000
there have been no further records of them appearing.

00:05:31.160 --> 00:05:32.040
Usually, they...

00:05:32.040 --> 00:05:34.079
would post updates online irregularly.

00:05:34.680 --> 00:05:35.800
But their recent behavior...

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:37.560
differs greatly from before.

00:05:38.199 --> 00:05:39.199
Don't you find that strange?

00:05:40.839 --> 00:05:41.600
Detective Qi.

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:44.600
Mr. Tan.

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:47.439
I didn't know Detective Qi was coming for tea today.

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:48.319
Otherwise,

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:49.639
I would have welcomed you personally.

00:05:54.879 --> 00:05:55.879
All right, all right.

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:57.759
The reason I came today...

00:05:57.759 --> 00:05:59.360
was specifically to find Mr. Zhao.

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:01.079
I didn't expect Mr. Tan to be here too.

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:02.759
That works out well.

00:06:03.680 --> 00:06:04.759
Let's have a chat.

00:06:05.319 --> 00:06:05.759
Ma Shan.

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:09.040
Regarding Ma Shan kidnapping the businessman...

00:06:09.519 --> 00:06:10.439
A Hai and I...

00:06:10.519 --> 00:06:11.360
have already discussed it.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:13.120
She lost her daughter,

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:14.000
which is truly pitiable.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:16.240
So we have decided...

00:06:16.759 --> 00:06:17.519
not to press charges against her.

00:06:18.439 --> 00:06:21.240
I remember you telling me, Mr. Tan,

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:23.480
that you are a wealthy heir from Han Cheng,

00:06:24.879 --> 00:06:26.040
and you came to Tai Cheng on a business trip.

00:06:26.040 --> 00:06:27.079
You were kidnapped,

00:06:27.079 --> 00:06:28.519
and then saved by Zhao Qishan.

00:06:29.160 --> 00:06:30.959
You two appreciated each other,

00:06:30.959 --> 00:06:32.319
and later you invested in him.

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:35.279
I specifically checked the archives.

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:37.519
I didn't find any of the...

00:06:37.519 --> 00:06:38.720
relevant information you mentioned.

00:06:42.839 --> 00:06:44.680
Mr. Tan doesn't seem to be from Han Cheng.

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:47.800
Detective Qi.

00:06:48.600 --> 00:06:50.720
What do you mean by saying this?

00:06:51.399 --> 00:06:52.319
I'm just curious.

00:06:54.079 --> 00:06:56.360
How could you all, in such a short time,

00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:58.120
weave such a fascinating story?

00:06:58.959 --> 00:06:59.959
Exactly how much of this...

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:02.360
is drawn from reality?

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:03.720
Detective Qi.

00:07:04.279 --> 00:07:05.920
If there is nothing else today,

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:07.360
let's end it here.

00:07:08.439 --> 00:07:09.519
Look at the state A Hai is in;

00:07:10.319 --> 00:07:11.240
he still needs to rest.

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:14.040
Show him out.

00:07:15.279 --> 00:07:15.600
Fine.

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:18.120
Then I won't disturb you further.

00:07:22.519 --> 00:07:22.920
By the way,

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:25.000
regarding Lin Niannian's disappearance,

00:07:25.240 --> 00:07:26.040
we have already opened a case.

00:07:26.920 --> 00:07:28.480
What does that have to do with us?

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:32.759
Detective Qi,

00:07:33.600 --> 00:07:35.360
investigating cases is police business.

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:37.319
You don't need to report to us.

00:07:37.839 --> 00:07:38.240
Of course.

00:07:39.600 --> 00:07:41.360
It's just that when we need your cooperation,

00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:42.680
I hope you can...

00:07:43.399 --> 00:07:44.839
stay right here, all in one piece.

00:07:45.399 --> 00:07:45.959
Don't move.

00:07:47.839 --> 00:07:48.839
Rest assured, Detective Qi.

00:07:49.399 --> 00:07:50.360
We will certainly cooperate.

00:08:09.519 --> 00:08:11.199
Having gone through a series of unpleasant events,

00:08:11.519 --> 00:08:12.920
I believe everyone just wants to...

00:08:12.920 --> 00:08:14.000
know the contents of the will as soon as possible.

00:08:14.920 --> 00:08:16.399
I won't keep everyone with pleasantries.

00:08:17.040 --> 00:08:18.279
Next, I will begin reading the will.

00:08:29.480 --> 00:08:29.720
Hello?

00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:30.160
Captain.

00:08:30.519 --> 00:08:32.320
I've obtained the copies of the wills you wanted.

00:08:32.679 --> 00:08:33.320
Two wills.

00:08:33.799 --> 00:08:35.120
One for each of the couple.

00:08:36.279 --> 00:08:37.639
The first will to be announced is...

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:39.039
Mr. Zhao Qishan's will.

00:08:39.480 --> 00:08:40.200
The testator,

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:41.000
Zhao Qishan,

00:08:41.639 --> 00:08:43.399
gifts all group shares to Tan Tian.

00:08:43.799 --> 00:08:44.960
He also set aside three sums of money.

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:46.000
Each sum is one hundred thousand yuan,

00:08:46.799 --> 00:08:47.720
distributed to Zhao Qihai,

00:08:47.919 --> 00:08:49.000
Fang Qiu, and A Si.

00:08:49.960 --> 00:08:51.519
The remaining 3.7 million-plus under his name,

00:08:51.519 --> 00:08:52.480
in cash and real estate,

00:08:52.600 --> 00:08:53.960
are all inherited by his wife, Li Ren.

00:08:54.559 --> 00:08:55.279
Li Ren's will...

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:57.440
leaves all assets to her biological sister,

00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:58.440
Li Ran.

00:09:09.879 --> 00:09:11.080
3.7 million in cash.

00:09:11.399 --> 00:09:12.960
How could Zhao Qishan only have this much?

00:09:14.200 --> 00:09:14.600
I...

00:09:17.799 --> 00:09:18.440
Enough.

00:09:18.799 --> 00:09:19.519
What do you mean, enough?

00:09:20.159 --> 00:09:21.639
It's easy for you to say.

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:24.519
At least you got all the group's shares.

00:09:24.799 --> 00:09:25.759
What about me?

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:27.639
Enough!

00:09:30.840 --> 00:09:31.720
My brother...

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:39.000
Jerk!

00:09:40.919 --> 00:09:41.519
Let me ask you.

00:09:42.159 --> 00:09:43.519
What the hell use are shares to me?

00:09:43.799 --> 00:09:45.720
Cash. I want cash.

00:09:46.279 --> 00:09:47.759
Zhao Qishan had all the cash.

00:09:48.039 --> 00:09:49.279
And now nobody knows where it's hidden.

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:14.039
A Si.

00:10:14.440 --> 00:10:15.559
Why are you still here?

00:10:17.679 --> 00:10:19.320
I told Zhao Qishan a long time ago.

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:21.039
To split up the money.

00:10:21.679 --> 00:10:23.200
And let everyone go lay low for a while.

00:10:23.879 --> 00:10:24.559
He wouldn't listen to me.

00:10:25.519 --> 00:10:26.679
Now he's suddenly dead.

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:28.799
The police are already suspicious of us.

00:10:31.600 --> 00:10:32.519
So tell me.

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:34.200
What do we do?

00:10:39.960 --> 00:10:40.799
I'm telling you.

00:10:42.080 --> 00:10:44.320
If they keep investigating Lin Niannian,

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:45.360
we're all done for.

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:47.360
Before that happens,

00:10:47.720 --> 00:10:49.080
we must find that money.

00:10:49.519 --> 00:10:51.200
Find it at all costs.

00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:51.879
Do you understand?